{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id7a854733-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s8321"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"8321"},"text":"§ 8321.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Authority to define terms","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id7a854734-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s8321/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Authority to define terms","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The Commodity Futures Trading Commission may adopt a rule to define—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id7a854735-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s8321/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the term “commercial risk”; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id7a854736-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s8321/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" any other term included in an amendment to the Commodity Exchange Act (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s1"},"text":"7 U.S.C. 1","children":[],"tail":" et seq.) made by this subtitle."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id7a854737-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s8321/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Modification of definitions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"To include transactions and entities that have been structured to evade this subtitle (or an amendment made by this subtitle), the Commodity Futures Trading Commission shall adopt a rule to further define the terms “swap”, “swap dealer”, “major swap participant”, and “eligible contract participant”.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id7a854738-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/203/tVII/s721/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–203, title VII, § 721(b)","children":[],"tail":", (c), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2010-07-21"},"text":"July 21, 2010","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/124/1670"},"text":"124 Stat. 1670","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id7a854739-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id7a85473a-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id7a85473b-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This subtitle, referred to in text, is subtitle A (§§ 711–754) of title VII of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/203"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–203","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2010-07-21"},"text":"July 21, 2010","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/124/1641"},"text":"124 Stat. 1641","children":[],"tail":", which enacted this subchapter, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s78c–2"},"text":"section 78c–2 of this title","children":[],"tail":", and sections 1b, 6b–1, 6r to 6t, 7b–3, 24a, and 26 of Title 7, Agriculture, amended sections 78f, 78"},{"tag":"i","attrib":{},"text":"o","children":[],"tail":", and 78s of this title, sections 1a, 2, 6 to 6b, 6c, 6d, 6m, 6q, 6s, 7 to 7b, 8 to 9a, 12, 12a, 13, 13–1, 13a–1, 13b, 15, 16, 21, 24, 25, 27 to 27b, 27e, and 27f of Title 7, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t11/s761"},"text":"section 761 of Title 11","children":[],"tail":", Bankruptcy, and sections 4421 and 4422 of Title 12, Banks and Banking, enacted provisions set out as notes under sections 1a, 2, 6a, 7a–1, 7a–3, and 9 of Title 7, and amended provisions set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s78c"},"text":"section 78c of this title","children":[],"tail":". For complete classification of subtitle A to the Code, see Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Commodity Exchange Act, referred to in subsec. (a)(2), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1922-09-21/ch369"},"text":"act Sept. 21, 1922, ch. 369","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/42/998"},"text":"42 Stat. 998","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to chapter 1 (§ 1 et seq.) of Title 7, Agriculture. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s1"},"text":"section 1 of Title 7","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"id7a85473c-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section is comprised of subsecs. (b) and (c) of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/203/s721"},"text":"section 721 of Pub. L. 111–203","children":[],"tail":", which were redesignated as subsecs. (a) and (b), respectively, of this section for purposes of codification."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
